metadata.name: BattleCats
metadata.description: BattleCats is a fighting MetaVerse where players create, play games, compete for prizes, and earn tokens. Genesis collection consists of 10k NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each BattleCat possesses traits and skills that make them impeccably unique and well prepared for battles in the Catosseum arena. Visit www.battlecatsnft.com to learn more.
